%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%

sequenceDiagram
autonumber

actor COE as COE Head
participant UI as Innovation UI
participant BFF as Innovation BFF
participant SERVICE as Innovation Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS Read schema"}
participant CACHE as Redis

COE ->> UI: Open Innovation Home
UI ->> BFF: Load COE review worklist

BFF ->> CACHE: Get COE review list
alt Cache Hit
    CACHE -->> BFF: Portfolio / Cohort review records
else Cache Miss
    BFF ->> SERVICE: getCOEReviewWorklist(coeUserId)
    SERVICE ->> READDB: Get portfolios/cohorts WHERE status IN ('Review','Live','Sent Back')
    READDB -->> SERVICE: Review worklist
    SERVICE -->> BFF: Worklist response
    BFF ->> CACHE: Cache COE review list
end

BFF -->> UI: Show portfolio/cohort list with status

COE ->> UI: Click Portfolio / Cohort
UI ->> BFF: Open review detail(entityId, entityType)

BFF ->> SERVICE: getReviewDetail(entityId, entityType)
SERVICE ->> READDB: Get details, ringi metadata, evaluation model, cohort list if portfolio
READDB -->> SERVICE: Read-only review data
SERVICE -->> BFF: Review detail payload
BFF -->> UI: Render Details, Ringi Details, Evaluation tabs in read-only mode